{"tid":1380403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候準備定九月罷課罷教！","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:12:52.000Z","uid":293188,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c8771e89a1b012059d2f1d4c7948dba7f8f6a5d4","tid":1380403,"uid":293188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:14:44.000Z","msg":"距離九月開學仲有一個月，以而家局勢落去，基本上中學大學一定要有罷課！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前嗌過幾次罷工都冇成功，因為搞罷課罷工同遊行唔同，唔係話一嗌就出到嚟。<br />\n我地要返學校/ 返公司準備、組織！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n八月可以做乜？<br />\n1) 收集文宣，向自己同學宣傳<br />\n2) 搞罷課聯署，等外界知有好多中學準備罷課<br />\n3) 夾實教協，要求佢地發動罷課<br />\n<br />\n我地要有真正罷課，而唔係2014年咁校方比學生放一兩日假。<br />\n要做到咁，老師罷教係十分重要！<br />\n而家連公務員都有可能罷工，教師點可以唔做嘢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老師罷教好需要教協做野，佢係一個八萬會員既工會（起碼名義上）<br />\n不過大家都知教協領導層咩料，向來都係同政府妥協。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n612之後教協出聲明嗌「罷課」，但根本冇動員過。<br />\n好多學校都有老師學生聯署反送中，但冇工會帶頭，會驚唔夠力量、驚冇左份工。<br />\n<br />\n我地應該去夾一夾教協，去教協辦事處做一次請願，要有老師同學生參與，一齊要求教協理事真真正正咁發動一次罷課。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全力去支援保護老師學生，團結起來先以可以阻止秋後算帳!<br />\n<br />\n小弟開左個TG ，大家可以入黎傾下：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/schstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fschstrike&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67YeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=5f06fc02\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/schstrike</a>"},{"pid":"f9be6893c44ff7c8cdaa32a1e6c572583cc78765","tid":1380403,"uid":293188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"自推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3ee7575475772b91e83bae5e840a81176faada","tid":1380403,"uid":228888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:47:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"e27af68c5351b4d2641f8961c52bd8b9bcdc0507","tid":1380403,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:49:13.000Z","msg":"好多奶共校長會秋後算賬"},{"pid":"7caa845b60778b216e6daec7544e762ecf2d89a7","tid":1380403,"uid":293188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"重推!!"}]}